# Crypto Bot

**Lightweight live trading bot for the Crypto Quant Ecosystem.**

Part of: [crypto-lab](https://github.com/11e3/crypto-lab) → [bt](https://github.com/11e3/bt) → **[crypto-bot](https://github.com/11e3/crypto-bot)** → [crypto-ml](https://github.com/11e3/crypto-ml)

